Class Polyline

java.lang.Object
  FIT_8201_Sviridov_Lines.Polyline

public class Polyline
extends java.lang.Object

Class representing polyline object. Encapsulates polyline type, thickness, color. Caches stroke object for faster drawing.

Author:
alstein
